    "schema:description": "Metadata harvested via Dataverse schema.org export API by Claude Code. Converted to CDIF discovery profile: Property names prefixed with schema: namespace; @context set to CDIF prefix declarations (extra prefixes preserved); @type values normalized to arrays with schema: prefix; schema:license wrapped in array; Distributions normalized; schema:creator wrapped in @list; Agent objects fixed (Person name synthesis, sameAs arrays). Removed redundant schema:author (identical to schema:creator); CDIF recommends schema:creator."
